<DIV1 TYPE="chapter">
<HEAD> DCXLVI.
<LB>
<FOREIGN LANG="LAT">Prelatus statuta sua servare debet.</FOREIGN></HEAD>

<P> Valerius tellis how one &thorn;at was calli&dtail; Licinius
ordan&dtail; a law, &thorn;at no ma&ntail; sul&dtail; by our 1 acre of
land; and he boght many ma.  And vnder grace of a fenyng he
excusy&dtail; hy&mtail; &thorn;erof &amp; gaff parte &thorn;eroff vnto
his so&ntail;.  And for &thorn;is he was accusy&dtail;, furst
&thorn;at he made a law &amp; chargi&dtail; it to be kepy&dtail;,
&amp; syne &thorn;at he was furste at brak it hy&mtail; selfe.

</P>
